org.jsweet.transpiler.extension.RemoveJavaDependenciesAdapter
org.jsweet.transpiler.extension.RemoveJavaDependenciesES6Adapter
public class RemoveJavaDependenciesES6Adapter extends RemoveJavaDependenciesAdapter
An adapter that removes many uses of Java APIs and replace them with JavaScript ES6 equivalent when possible.
